Introduction

XENO-T (Korean: 제노티; Japanese: ゼノ-T) (formerly known as Topp Dogg (탑독)) debuted under Stardom Entertainment on October 22, 2013, which now merged under HUNUS Entertainment. On February 21, Hunus Entertainment announced that the five members Sangdo, Hojoon, B-Joo, Xero, Sangwon will now promote under the group name XENO-T. They are currently promoting in Japan.
